  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/18d46c5c7b54a94df81bce2c9f2f9aae.webp?t=1654872920\" width=127 height=35 /></span><br>Bomb, Sumo, Shield and many more, customize the gameplay of your ghost with all the different classes of the game. You just need to choose your class and your skin, take your ghost into battle and face off your friends!<br><br>En collaboration avec Studio M!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/d02b826b881cd8a68da253a977507167.poster.avif?t=1654872920\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/d02b826b881cd8a68da253a977507167.webm?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/d02b826b881cd8a68da253a977507167.mp4?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/2b21e17d3a357517638f24226a1b6b61.webp?t=1654872920\" width=172 height=35 /></span><br>Push your enemies into the various traps of the map!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/61fcaea91f46d3887765478832bddb88.poster.avif?t=1654872920\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/61fcaea91f46d3887765478832bddb88.webm?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/61fcaea91f46d3887765478832bddb88.mp4?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/ae778fcc073ad13b6cffa0635b309e07.webp?t=1654872920\" width=220 height=35 /></span><br>Be the first to take a power up and defeat your ennemis with all the crazy tactics you can imagine!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/51a182e3611294a2c1111e34bd47782b.poster.avif?t=1654872920\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/51a182e3611294a2c1111e34bd47782b.webm?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/51a182e3611294a2c1111e34bd47782b.mp4?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/4b3581747b6b33833f236d3abcf58182.webp?t=1654872920\" width=256 height=35 /></span><br>Play up to four with your friends and compete until victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/1101b0adfd2173d92e25d8c31d9b4903.poster.avif?t=1654872920\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/1101b0adfd2173d92e25d8c31d9b4903.webm?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/1101b0adfd2173d92e25d8c31d9b4903.mp4?t=1654872920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/90f9848ccb439f8d545ba1851c72abe2.webp?t=1654872920\" width=216 height=35 /></span><br>Tamashi Party is best enjoyed with controllers. We used computer & switch controller to play.<br>Remote Play Together over steam to enjoy a party with your friends at every moment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/95ef447d730277739c3f00800e385365.webp?t=1654872920\" width=283 height=35 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1954390/extras/2ff7c8fd01fd317e1303a8fcc483a864.avif?t=1654872920\" width=616 height=206 /></span>",
